highlights.text: “Don't You Want Me - KI/KI Remix” by Felix and KI/KI is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Australia, up 13 spots at #66.
KPop Demon Hunters Cast has the most spots on Viral Songs Australia. “Golden” is the highest at #21.
“Nice To Each Other” by Olivia Dean has been on Viral Songs Australia the longest, at 105 days straight.
“What a Difference a Day Makes (from the Netflix Limited Series "Black Rabbit")” by RAYE is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Australia at #100.
